<HEADLINE>
FT  06 APR 94 / London Stock Exchange: New highs and lows for 1994
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
   By STEVE THOMPSON, JOEL KIBAZO and PETER JOHN
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
NEW HIGHS (29).
