growth in the sales of data and graphics projectors, which form a core part
of Barco's business.
However, conditions elsewhere had been harder, the group said, with an 11
per cent growth in turnover in the US market and 4 per cent fall in Europe.
Although the climate for investment remained weak in Europe, prospects in
Asia and South and North America were 'exceptionally' encouraging, the
company said. It added that it expected to record a similar level of growth
next year.
